#. module: google_gmail
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/google_gmail/models/fetchmail_server.py:0
msgid ""
"Connect your Gmail account with the OAuth Authentication process. \n"
"You will be redirected to the Gmail login page where you will need to accept "
"the permission."
msgstr ""
"Forbind din Gmail-konto via OAuth-godkendelsesprocessen.\n"
"Du bliver omdirigeret til Gmail-login, hvor du skal acceptere tilladelsen."

#. module: google_gmail
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/google_gmail/models/ir_mail_server.py:0
msgid ""
"Connect your Gmail account with the OAuth Authentication process.  \n"
"By default, only a user with a matching email address will be able to use "
"this server. To extend its use, you should set a \"mail.default.from\" "
"system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Forbind din Gmail-konto via OAuth-godkendelsesprocessen.  \n"
"Som standard kan kun én bruger med en matchende e-mailadresse bruge denne "
"server. Hvis flere skal kunne bruge den, skal du indstille systemparameteren "
"\"mail.default.from\"."

